{"tid":1829500,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黑夜裡數百公尺外也能認出你是誰，美軍新科技讓人戴面具也無所遁形","createTime":"2020-01-18T19:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T19:39:48.000Z","uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"716052a235da2f9677da4e7c4a4202456a08d352","tid":1829500,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T19:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/15115654/heat-87276_1280-624x486.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F15115654%2Fheat-87276_1280-624x486.jpg&h=f9c0fc1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臉部辨識應用已十分廣泛，除了手機臉部解鎖，還被警察用於日常執法，但臉部辨識也有很多限制，只有在演唱會安檢這樣光線固定的場景，才能精確辨識。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/15111942/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A9%E7%9C%BC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F15111942%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%259C%25BC.jpg&h=680ac9a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果是黑夜又遠在十公尺外，臉部辨識技術往往就無能為力了。不過目前美軍正在開發新的臉部辨識技術，可在夜晚遠距辨識臉部，所用的原理也十分常見，就是熱成像技術。<br />\n<br />\n這種技術在軍事領域十分普遍，夜視鏡用的就是這種。熱成像儀與相機等可見光成像不同，能辨識物體產生的熱輻射，形成不同的紅外線圖像。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/15110506/thermal-and-visible-imaging-sensor.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F15110506%2Fthermal-and-visible-imaging-sensor.jpg&h=1af26a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但僅透過熱成像辨識一個人的身分十分困難，夜視儀一般只能辨識目標是否活體，紅外線圖像的臉部輪廓也十分模糊，因此很難判斷對方是誰。<br />\n<br />\n那美軍怎麼使用熱成像儀辨識人呢？The Register 曾報導，美國陸軍研究實驗室採用基於 AI 的圖像合成方法，從模糊的臉部紅外線圖像提取眼睛、鼻子、嘴唇等特徵，再透過演算法還原成類似素描的人像圖片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/15110557/1-newarmytechn-e1579057603191.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F15110557%2F1-newarmytechn-e1579057603191.jpg&h=ac624b76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n研究人員選取 60 人的可見光臉部圖像和紅外線臉部圖像構建資料庫並試驗，結果發現採用這種方式辨識準確率可達 80% 以上。<br />\n<br />\n不過市場成熟臉部辨識技術的準確率都超過 99%，80% 精準度距離實際應用還有一段距離，但這種技術在其他方面比一般臉部辨識有不少優勢。<br />\n<br />\n透過熱成像儀技術臉部辨識，就不用擔心受光照條件影響，比起可見光臉部辨識，熱成像儀也更不容易受化妝、面具等因素影響。之前一家美國 AI 公司用 3D 面具騙過多個臉部辨識系統，而熱成像儀能直接「看穿」面具下的臉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/15110814/3D-masks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F15110814%2F3D-masks.jpg&h=b6c7afb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年美軍還在熱成像儀臉部辨識技術增加投入，據美國國防部的財政數據，去年 9 月美軍與 Polaris Sensor Technologies 熱成像儀技術公司簽訂一份 450 萬美元合約，請這家公司幫忙開發此技術，整個計畫會持續到 2021 年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/15111204/Polaris-Sensor-Technologies_Thermographic-camera-product.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F15111204%2FPolaris-Sensor-Technologies_Thermographic-camera-product.jpg&h=a78c66de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相關文件顯示，美軍希望這種技術能在多種遮擋條件下完成臉部辨識，如汽車擋風玻璃、背光或大霧等場景，同時還要整合到足以便攜的個人裝置，能在 10~500 公尺的距離辨識。<br />\n<br />\nPolaris Sensor Technologies 在熱成像儀領域的技術積累很多，其中一項專門用於紅外線臉部辨識的專利，能透過演算法大幅提升紅外線圖像的辨識準確率。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/15111747/Infrared-face-recognition.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F15111747%2FInfrared-face-recognition.jpg&h=3873be26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了應付夜晚、遠距離等不便臉部辨識的場景，除了熱成像儀臉部辨識，美軍甚至嘗試利用心跳遠距離辨識人。<br />\n<br />\n據 MIT Technology Review 報導，五角大樓（The Pentagon）已經研發出一種新設備「Jetso」，可在 200 公尺內透過「雷射振動測量」技術檢測心跳引起的表面運動，因為心臟特徵像虹膜無法改變和偽裝，可能用以辨識不同個體。<br />\n<br />\n如果這些技術更成熟，那麼執法機構捕捉罪犯的效率會大大提高，但也意味著臉部辨識系統在日常生活更難察覺，如果使用這項技術的人和機構沒有受完整的監管，後果會頗為可怕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2020/01/16/us-army-thermography/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2Fus-army-thermography%2F&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1Cq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=5bfc0530\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2020/01/16/us-army-thermography/</a><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/01/19/B3SDOW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F01%2F19%2FB3SDOW.png&h=1967c39f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba156a0b578131bf0501fcf8ab434fc6d3da4890","tid":1829500,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T19:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce9a7789e5b13c68268394a5de9f9180c46feb0","tid":1829500,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T19:20:39.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"f9ce152e732bbc1887b3088e694728a35d7194a7","tid":1829500,"uid":127735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T19:22:52.000Z","msg":"有時科技愈進步都唔係一定好"},{"pid":"d7435cdc0843ff989945529bb405c8bb64be7187","tid":1829500,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T19:24:42.000Z","msg":"信美國一定好過信中國<br />\n<br />\n畢竟ios同android已經融入生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1415d8cf11835acb7c0f8a233cced3c6a6dda76","tid":1829500,"uid":79081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T19:25:11.000Z","msg":"公開=已過時"},{"pid":"2b6d8d8f425f5a2674a76f8953c69784b633a033","tid":1829500,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9ce152e732bbc1887b3088e694728a35d7194a7","tid":1829500,"uid":127735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T19:22:52.000Z","msg":"有時科技愈進步都唔係一定好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T19:35:55.000Z","msg":"睇下邊個用"},{"pid":"790c88ae4bec46b482fc0e020f0d0b72a542d570","tid":1829500,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T19:37:15.000Z","msg":"據 MIT Technology Review 報導，五角大樓（The Pentagon）已經研發出一種新設備「Jetso」，可在 200 公尺內透過「雷射振動測量」技術檢測心跳引起的表面運動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f76659c5f74708a56baea857a5efc2650b55ea4","tid":1829500,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T19:37:45.000Z","msg":"著衫都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ae79a1ac88c2f284752ab6ba6409ce3d889426","tid":1829500,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T19:37:52.000Z","msg":"保鮮紙包面"},{"pid":"88fdcfcc791cef833546af57262e184f40f9b179","tid":1829500,"uid":189328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T19:39:48.000Z","msg":"中共聽到應該好興奮又有新技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n差在今次用咩方法偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}